{"video_id": "t0n-zxIsnfQ", "title": "The Divine Pastimes of Srivasa Thakura | Sri Gaura Mandala Parikrama 2024 | HH Stoka Krishna Swami", "speaker": "HH Stoka Krishna Swami", "youtube_url": "https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=t0n-zxIsnfQ", "duration": 457, "segments": [{"start": 0.0, "end": 25.0, "text": " Sri Gauranga"}, {"start": 25.0, "end": 26.84, "text": " Sri Gauranga"}, {"start": 26.84, "end": 36.84, "text": " Sri Gauranga"}, {"start": 36.84, "end": 46.84, "text": " Sri Gauranga"}, {"start": 46.84, "end": 55.84, "text": " Sri Gauranga"}, {"start": 55.84, "end": 56.84, "text": " Sri Gauranga"}, {"start": 56.84, "end": 57.84, "text": " Sri Gauranga"}, {"start": 57.84, "end": 58.84, "text": " Sri Gauranga"}, {"start": 58.84, "end": 59.84, "text": " Sri Gauranga"}, {"start": 59.84, "end": 60.84, "text": " Sri Gauranga"}, {"start": 60.84, "end": 61.84, "text": " Sri Gauranga"}, {"start": 61.84, "end": 62.84, "text": " Sri Gauranga"}, {"start": 62.84, "end": 63.84, "text": " Sri Gauranga"}, {"start": 63.84, "end": 64.84, "text": " Sri Gauranga"}, {"start": 64.84, "end": 65.84, "text": " Sri Gauranga"}, {"start": 65.84, "end": 66.84, "text": " Sri Gauranga"}, {"start": 66.84, "end": 67.84, "text": " Sri Gauranga"}, {"start": 67.84, "end": 68.84, "text": " Sri Gauranga"}, {"start": 68.84, "end": 69.84, "text": " Sri Gauranga"}, {"start": 69.84, "end": 70.84, "text": " Sri Gauranga"}, {"start": 70.84, "end": 71.84, "text": " Sri Gauranga"}, {"start": 71.84, "end": 72.84, "text": " Sri Gauranga"}, {"start": 72.84, "end": 73.84, "text": " Sri Gauranga"}, {"start": 73.84, "end": 74.84, "text": " Sri Gauranga"}, {"start": 74.84, "end": 75.84, "text": " Sri Gauranga"}, {"start": 75.84, "end": 76.84, "text": " Sri Gauranga"}, {"start": 76.84, "end": 77.84, "text": " Sri Gauranga"}, {"start": 77.84, "end": 78.84, "text": " Sri Gauranga"}, {"start": 78.84, "end": 79.84, "text": " Sri Gauranga"}, {"start": 79.84, "end": 80.84, "text": " Sri Gauranga"}, {"start": 80.84, "end": 81.84, "text": " Sri Gauranga"}, {"start": 81.84, "end": 82.84, "text": " Sri Gauranga"}, {"start": 82.84, "end": 83.84, "text": " Sri Gauranga"}, {"start": 83.84, "end": 84.84, "text": " Sri Gauranga"}, {"start": 84.84, "end": 85.84, "text": " Sri Gauranga"}, {"start": 85.84, "end": 86.84, "text": " Sri Gauranga"}, {"start": 86.84, "end": 92.84, "text": " Sri Srivas Pandit is described as the incarnation of Narada Muni."}, {"start": 92.84, "end": 100.84, "text": " Through Srivas Thakur, Lord Chaitanya taught that he is conquered by the love of his devotees"}, {"start": 100.84, "end": 107.84, "text": " and how anyone who is dear to his devotee also conquers his heart."}, {"start": 107.84, "end": 113.84, "text": " Srivas Pandit appeared at Biyani Bazar in Shilha district"}, {"start": 113.84, "end": 117.84, "text": " as the second son of Sri Jaladhar Pandit."}, {"start": 117.84, "end": 122.84, "text": " It is mentioned in Chaitanya Charita Amrita that Srivas had three brothers"}, {"start": 122.84, "end": 125.84, "text": " Sri Rama, Sri Pati and Sri Nidhi."}, {"start": 125.84, "end": 130.84, "text": " But Jaladhar Pandit had an older son named Nalina Pandita"}, {"start": 130.84, "end": 133.84, "text": " who disappeared when the family lived in Biyani Bazar."}, {"start": 133.84, "end": 141.84, "text": " When Srivas was 12 years old, Jaladhar took his family to Navadvipa and remained there."}, {"start": 141.84, "end": 142.84, "text": " Because of this,"}, {"start": 142.84, "end": 147.84, "text": " because young Nimai Pandit seemed to have grown arrogant by his scholarship,"}, {"start": 147.84, "end": 149.84, "text": " one day Srivas told him,"}, {"start": 149.84, "end": 155.84, "text": " why do you people undertake study so that they might understand what is devotion to Sri Krishna?"}, {"start": 155.84, "end": 159.84, "text": " If by scholarship one does not gain such devotion,"}, {"start": 159.84, "end": 162.84, "text": " then how will that learning help him?"}, {"start": 162.84, "end": 168.84, "text": " It simply becomes a tedious endeavour which in the end is nothing but a waste of time."}, {"start": 168.84, "end": 171.84, "text": " If you have actually learned something,"}, {"start": 171.84, "end": 175.84, "text": " then begin your worship of Sri Krishna now."}, {"start": 175.84, "end": 178.84, "text": " Nimai laughed and replied,"}, {"start": 178.84, "end": 181.84, "text": " by your mercy certainly that will come to be."}, {"start": 181.84, "end": 184.84, "text": " If you are all kind enough to me,"}, {"start": 184.84, "end": 188.84, "text": " then definitely I shall attain devotion to Sri Krishna's lotus feet."}, {"start": 188.84, "end": 190.84, "text": " Shortly thereafter,"}, {"start": 190.84, "end": 192.84, "text": " Mahaprabhu journeyed to Gaya"}, {"start": 192.84, "end": 197.84, "text": " where he accepted initiation from Sri Eswara Puri."}, {"start": 197.84, "end": 200.84, "text": " The Lord did so to teach that,"}, {"start": 200.84, "end": 203.84, "text": " without the blessings and guidance of great souls"}, {"start": 203.84, "end": 206.84, "text": " and without the prayers of great Vaishnavas,"}, {"start": 206.84, "end": 209.84, "text": " beseeching Krishna to extend his mercy to us,"}, {"start": 209.84, "end": 214.84, "text": " there is no hope of our really receiving the mercy of Krishna."}, {"start": 214.84, "end": 216.84, "text": " Lord Krishna was born in Mathura"}, {"start": 216.84, "end": 219.84, "text": " but performed his most intimate pastimes in Vrindavan."}, {"start": 219.84, "end": 221.84, "text": " Similarly,"}, {"start": 221.84, "end": 225.84, "text": " Sri Chaitanya Mahaprabhu was born in the house of Jagannath Mishra,"}, {"start": 225.84, "end": 229.84, "text": " yet he performed his most intimate pastimes in the house of Srivas Thakur."}, {"start": 230.84, "end": 236.84, "text": " One night while Lord Gauranga was engaged in Kirtan,"}, {"start": 236.84, "end": 240.84, "text": " the son of Srivas Thakur who was suffering from fever left his body."}, {"start": 240.84, "end": 243.84, "text": " The lady started weeping very loudly."}, {"start": 243.84, "end": 245.84, "text": " Srivas Thakur on hearing the news,"}, {"start": 245.84, "end": 249.84, "text": " quickly ran into the room and found his son's dead body."}, {"start": 249.84, "end": 252.84, "text": " He told the ladies to give up this crime"}, {"start": 252.84, "end": 254.84, "text": " that there should be no grief,"}, {"start": 254.84, "end": 259.84000000000003, "text": " that even a most sinful person who dies while hearing the holy name"}, {"start": 259.84000000000003, "end": 262.84000000000003, "text": " and glories of Krishna will be liberated."}, {"start": 262.84000000000003, "end": 263.84000000000003, "text": " He told them,"}, {"start": 263.84000000000003, "end": 266.84000000000003, "text": " My son is so fortunate to have left his body"}, {"start": 266.84000000000003, "end": 271.84000000000003, "text": " hearing the harinam and kirtan of Lord Chaitanya and his devotees."}, {"start": 271.84000000000003, "end": 275.84000000000003, "text": " Now if you wish to cry, do it silently in your own heart."}, {"start": 275.84000000000003, "end": 277.84000000000003, "text": " But do not tell anyone what has happened"}, {"start": 277.84000000000003, "end": 282.84000000000003, "text": " because if you disturb the ecstatic dancing of my Lord Gauranga,"}, {"start": 282.84000000000003, "end": 287.84000000000003, "text": " then I will tie a pot around my neck and drown myself in the Ganges today."}, {"start": 289.84000000000003, "end": 293.84000000000003, "text": " After speaking all these words, Srivas Thakur went back into the kirtan"}, {"start": 293.84000000000003, "end": 298.84000000000003, "text": " and with a big smile on his face began dancing with Lord Chaitanya and Vaishnavas."}, {"start": 298.84000000000003, "end": 302.84000000000003, "text": " The kirtan went on throughout the entire night."}, {"start": 302.84000000000003, "end": 306.84000000000003, "text": " When Mahaprabhu came to know of the passing of Srivas' son,"}, {"start": 306.84000000000003, "end": 309.84000000000003, "text": " he cried tears of love and said,"}, {"start": 309.84000000000003, "end": 315.84000000000003, "text": " How could I ever leave the association of such a pure devotee as Srivas Thakur?"}, {"start": 315.84000000000003, "end": 318.84000000000003, "text": " He loves me so much that he does not even express his gratitude."}, {"start": 318.84000000000003, "end": 323.84000000000003, "text": " He does not even express his grief over the death of his own son."}, {"start": 323.84000000000003, "end": 327.84000000000003, "text": " Mahaprabhu gave this benediction to Srivas."}, {"start": 327.84000000000003, "end": 330.84000000000003, "text": " There will never be poverty in your house."}, {"start": 330.84000000000003, "end": 332.84000000000003, "text": " If you simply remain indoors,"}, {"start": 332.84000000000003, "end": 337.84000000000003, "text": " whatever you require for your worship will come to your door."}, {"start": 337.84000000000003, "end": 343.84000000000003, "text": " At present, ISKCON is serving the temple at the birth site of Srivas Pandit."}, {"start": 343.84000000000003, "end": 345.84000000000003, "text": " There is also an ancient temple"}, {"start": 345.84000000000003, "end": 347.84000000000003, "text": " where the deity of Vasudev"}, {"start": 347.84000000000003, "end": 351.84000000000003, "text": " was established in the 7th century."}, {"start": 351.84000000000003, "end": 353.84000000000003, "text": " It is still being worshipped."}, {"start": 353.84000000000003, "end": 355.84000000000003, "text": " Okay, another prana mantra."}, {"start": 355.84000000000003, "end": 356.84000000000003, "text": " It is there with the translation."}, {"start": 356.84000000000003, "end": 358.84000000000003, "text": " So let us repeat this."}, {"start": 358.84000000000003, "end": 362.84000000000003, "text": " Srivas Pandita"}, {"start": 362.84000000000003, "end": 366.84000000000003, "text": " Dhimanyaha"}, {"start": 366.84000000000003, "end": 368.84000000000003, "text": " Pura"}, {"start": 368.84000000000003, "end": 372.84000000000003, "text": " Narado Munihi"}, {"start": 372.84000000000003, "end": 375.84000000000003, "text": " Parvatakhyo"}, {"start": 375.84000000000003, "end": 377.84000000000003, "text": " Munivaro"}, {"start": 377.84000000000003, "end": 380.84000000000003, "text": " Yaha"}, {"start": 380.84000000000003, "end": 382.84000000000003, "text": " Asi"}, {"start": 382.84000000000003, "end": 386.84000000000003, "text": " Narada Priyaha"}, {"start": 386.84000000000003, "end": 390.84000000000003, "text": " Sri Rama Panditaha"}, {"start": 390.84000000000003, "end": 394.84000000000003, "text": " Sriman"}, {"start": 394.84000000000003, "end": 397.84000000000003, "text": " Tatkanishtha"}, {"start": 397.84000000000003, "end": 401.84000000000003, "text": " Sahodaraha"}, {"start": 401.84000000000003, "end": 404.84000000000003, "text": " Namna"}, {"start": 404.84000000000003, "end": 406.84000000000003, "text": " Ambika"}, {"start": 406.84000000000003, "end": 407.84000000000003, "text": " Vraja"}, {"start": 407.84000000000003, "end": 408.84000000000003, "text": " Vraja"}, {"start": 408.84000000000003, "end": 410.84000000000003, "text": " Dhatri"}, {"start": 410.84000000000003, "end": 411.84000000000003, "text": " Dhatri"}, {"start": 411.84000000000003, "end": 412.84000000000003, "text": " Sthanyadhatri"}, {"start": 412.84000000000003, "end": 413.84000000000003, "text": " Sthanyadhatri"}, {"start": 413.84000000000003, "end": 414.84000000000003, "text": " Sthitapura"}, {"start": 414.84000000000003, "end": 415.84000000000003, "text": " Sthitapura"}, {"start": 415.84000000000003, "end": 416.84000000000003, "text": " Sthitapura"}, {"start": 416.84000000000003, "end": 417.84000000000003, "text": " Saiveyam"}, {"start": 417.84000000000003, "end": 418.84000000000003, "text": " Saiveyam"}, {"start": 418.84000000000003, "end": 419.84000000000003, "text": " Saiveyam"}, {"start": 419.84000000000003, "end": 420.84000000000003, "text": " Malini"}, {"start": 420.84000000000003, "end": 421.84000000000003, "text": " Malini"}, {"start": 421.84000000000003, "end": 422.84000000000003, "text": " Namni"}, {"start": 422.84000000000003, "end": 423.84000000000003, "text": " Namni"}, {"start": 423.84000000000003, "end": 425.84000000000003, "text": " Srivasagrihini"}, {"start": 425.84000000000003, "end": 427.84000000000003, "text": " Srivasagrihini"}, {"start": 427.84000000000003, "end": 428.84000000000003, "text": " Mata"}, {"start": 428.84000000000003, "end": 430.84000000000003, "text": " Mata"}, {"start": 430.84000000000003, "end": 434.84000000000003, "text": " Mata or Mata?"}, {"start": 434.84000000000003, "end": 440.84000000000003, "text": " Śrīvās is Nārada who plays such an important part in Kṛṣṇa's līlā."}, {"start": 440.84000000000003, "end": 446.84000000000003, "text": " Nārada Muni's friend Parvata Muni appeared as Śrīvās's younger brother, Ramāya."}, {"start": 446.84000000000003, "end": 453.84000000000003, "text": " Śrīvās's wife Mālini Devi was Kṛṣṇa's vet nurse in Vraja, Ambika."}]}